### =============================================================================
### xstravels-ext — extension tests
###
### Runs against the standalone `cds watch` on this project (port 4006).
### The reference server bootstrap in `srv/server.js` wires `submitForReview`
### to call the `validateReview` extension point, so any edits you make to
### `srv/TravelExtensionService/on-validateReview.js` fire immediately after
### `cds watch` reloads — no `cds push` needed for local iteration.
###
### To go all the way to a real tenant push, follow the flow described in
### the Exercise 5 workshop file.
### =============================================================================

@app = http://localhost:4006

### 1. Find an Open travel with low TotalPrice (cheap → passes any budget policy)
GET {{app}}/odata/v4/travel/Travels?$top=3&$select=ID,Status_code,TotalPrice&$filter=Status_code eq 'O' and TotalPrice lt 1000
Authorization: Basic alice:

### 2. Find an Open travel with high TotalPrice (blocked once a budget policy is in place)
GET {{app}}/odata/v4/travel/Travels?$top=3&$select=ID,Status_code,TotalPrice&$filter=Status_code eq 'O' and TotalPrice gt 10000
Authorization: Basic alice:

### 3. Submit a cheap travel for review — SUCCEEDS
###    Replace <LOW_ID> with an ID from request 1.
POST {{app}}/odata/v4/travel/Travels(ID=<LOW_ID>,IsActiveEntity=true)/TravelService.submitForReview
Authorization: Basic alice:
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 4. Submit an expensive travel for review
###    Replace <HIGH_ID> with an ID from request 2.
###
###    - Stub handler (default): SUCCEEDS silently. Status flips to InReview.
###    - After you enable the > 10000 policy in on-validateReview.js:
###        HTTP 409  {"message":"Total price ... exceeds policy limit ..."}
POST {{app}}/odata/v4/travel/Travels(ID=<HIGH_ID>,IsActiveEntity=true)/TravelService.submitForReview
Authorization: Basic alice:
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 5. Re-read the status of the expensive travel to confirm
GET {{app}}/odata/v4/travel/Travels?$filter=ID eq <HIGH_ID>&$select=ID,Status_code,TotalPrice
Authorization: Basic alice:
